This script can be used to download the SecTalks indexed here https://github.com/PaulSec/awesome-sec-talks But its not just limited to these indexed youtube videos. You can modify this(add any youtube playlist or single videos) according to your needs. 

usage: massSecVidDl.py [-h] [-l LINK] [-p PLAYLIST] [-s]

Youtube video download tool

optional arguments:
  -h, --help            Show this help message and exit
  -l LINK, --link LINK  Single youtube video to download
  -p PLAYLIST, --playlist PLAYLIST
                        Youtube playlist url to download all videos
  -s, --sec             All sec-talk videos


